{"type":"message","id":"c377586e","parentId":"e8510fb2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T10:11:54.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的！帮你们生成小程序的头像、简称和介绍。🦞\n\n我先用 AI 生成一个五金行业风格的 Logo 头像，然后给你写好简介文案。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b37b3400b5b1406bb4bfe221","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/yintong-hardware/images && cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/yintong-hardware/images && cat > logo_prompt.txt << 'EOF'\n生成一个简洁专业的企业 Logo，要求：\n- 主题：五金配件、机械制造\n- 元素：齿轮、螺丝、金属零件的抽象组合\n- 风格：简约、现代、工业风\n- 颜色：蓝色 + 银灰色（专业、可靠）\n- 形状：正方形，适合做小程序头像\n- 文字：可以包含\"银通\"或\"YT\"字母\n- 背景：纯色或渐变，不要太复杂\n- 用途：微信小程序头像（500x500px）\nEOF\ncat logo_prompt.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":63123,"output":225,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63348,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774260705028}}
